title: 10x FY19 Impact Report
subtitle: 10x FY19 Impact Report
excerpt: In our FY19 impact report, we reflect on five years since the creation of the fund that supports 10x investments–The Digital Services Fund. We cover the history of the efforts that led to today’s 10x program and our meetings with real venture capital investment firms to see what we can learn from our private sector peers. Projects showcased include the _U.S. Data Federation_ and the _Eligibility API’s Initiative_.
